    <item>
      <title>中国考虑取消主要购房限制以刺激需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/china-weighs-removing-major-homebuying-curbs-to-boost-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，由于之前的措施未能提振低迷的房地产市场，中国正考虑取消部分剩余的最重要的购房限制措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/china-weighs-removing-major-homebuying-curbs-to-boost-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 03:15:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
